name: magnificence of desert VII
description: This image was taken at the Khara Desert, Isfahan Province, Iran. Very silent Khara sand dunes make the landscape spectacular and a great place for meditation or jogging in the desert. at a very windy day, I could hardly saw my friend is walking through the sand dunes. so I managed myself on the wind, saw the scene through the viewfinder of my camera, and finally captured this moment of the magnificence of the desert.
